---
import conversation from "../../public/icons/conversation.svg";
import proposal from "../../public/icons/proposal.svg";
import code from "../../public/icons/code.svg";
import rocket from "../../public/icons/rocket.svg";
---

<div class="mainContainer">
    <h1>Is Your Web Presence Working For You?</h1>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="textContainer">
            <p class="mainText">Is your website designed to captivate potential customers seeking the services you offer? Does it seamlessly adapt to any device, ensuring a flawless user experience? In today's digital landscape, having a responsive and accessible website is no longer a luxuryâ€”it's a necessity.</p>
            <p class="mainText">My mission is to deliver top-notch, responsive, and accessible websites to small businesses and individuals in our community. Whether you're in need of a brand-new website or a revamp to thrive in the mobile era, I'm here to assist you. I specialize in creating a virtual hub where interested parties can discover and engage with your unique offerings. How may I be of service to you today?</p>
        </div>
        <div class="features">
            <article>
                <img src={conversation} alt="a picture of two chat bubbles from either direction indicating a conversation.">
                <div class="content">
                    <h3>1. Consultation</h3>
                    <p>It starts with a conversation where we'll determine what your project is about.</p>
                </div>
            </article>
            <article>
                <img src={proposal} alt="a picture of a pen and paper representing a proposal.">
                <div class="content">
                    <h3>2. Proposal</h3>
                    <p>A detailed project proposal will be presented, followed by an action plan.</p>
                </div>
            </article>
            <article>
                <img src={code} alt="a picture of a left carrat, forward slash and a right carrat.">
                <div class="content">
                    <h3>3. Creation</h3>
                    <p>Clients receive regular status updates as I work on and test the project.</p>
                </div>
            </article>
            <article>
                <img src={rocket} alt="a picture of a rocket.">
                <div class="content">
                    <h3>4. Launch</h3>
                    <p>Your product comes to life with value added and peace of mind. </p>
                </div>
            </article>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .container{
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: row;
		justify-content: center;
		align-items: center;
        gap: 1em;
        padding: 1em;
    }

    .textContainer{
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 1em;
        width: 50%;
        height: auto:
    }

    .mainText{
        font-size: 2.2rem;
        text-align: justify;
    }

    .features{
        width:50%;
    }

    .textContainer,
    .features{
        padding: 1em;
    }

    .content{
        width:50%;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: space-evenly;
        align-items: flex-start;
        padding: 1em;
        gap: 1em;
    }

    h1{
        font-size: 4em;
        font-weight: bold;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 1em 0;
    }

    h3{
        font-size: 2.5em;
        font-weight: bold;
    }

    p{
		background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
        padding: 1em;
        border: 1px solid rgba(186, 55, 47, 0.5); 
        border-radius: 0.4em;
        font-size: 1.5em;
        line-height: 1.2;
    }

    article{
        width: 100%;
        max-height: 100%;
        display:flex;
        flex-direction: row;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 1em;
    }

    img {
        width:10%;
        max-height: 100%;
    }
    
	@media screen and (max-width: 1080px){
		.mainContainer{
			flex-direction: column;
			justify-content: center;
			align-items: center;
		}

        .container{
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1em;
        }

        .textContainer,
        .features{
            width:100%;
        }
	}
</style>